Cypress Automation Test - Basic Website Navigation

Overview

This project demonstrates a basic automated test using Cypress.

The test validates if a webpage loads correctly by navigating to a specified URL.

Tool Used
- Cypress

Test Description
The test script opens a webpage and verifies that it loads successfully.

Test Script

describe('My first test', () => {
  it('visits a website', () => {
    cy.visit('https://example.com')
  })
})

Expected Result
The webpage should load successfully without errors.

Actual Result
The webpage loaded successfully, displaying the "Example Domain" page.

Status
Passed
